{"type": "article", "id": 53054, "title": "想用绿植做空间隔断，这款种植器可能会帮到你｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-10T23:16:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 24109, "name": "Paul Matter"}, {"id": 48561, "name": "Tait"}, {"id": 50140, "name": "Fabbrica Pelletterie Milano"}, {"id": 50141, "name": "Expormim"}, {"id": 50142, "name": "Adam Goodrum"}, {"id": 50143, "name": "Marc Sadler"}, {"id": 44901, "name": "Jaime Hayon"}, {"id": 50144, "name": "Thomas Mayfried"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 246, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180510224649hjgErwkSaiBvlZK5.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s9 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>SeaBubbles </h3><p>SeaBubbles 是一家法国公司提出的未来派零排放新型水上出租车解决方案，设计开发的前提，是不影响环境，或对城市基础设施不会造成任何负担。上个月，SeaBubbles 在日内瓦湖上测试了最新的原型，目前正在巴黎进行为期五周的试验，公司希望能在四年内为巴黎居民提供一个全新的水上交通工具。</p><p>SeaBubbles 的特点在于其水翼使用了特殊材料，会在船达到一定的速度时把船身抬离水面，大大减少水的阻力和增加航行速度，号称“零噪音、零波浪和零排放”，对环境影响较小。此外，SeaBubbles 还将配备 ABB Ability™船舶咨询系统 OCTOPUS，可帮助船员收集和分析所有相关数据，优化水上航行。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0641p3mugx&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224729JxY8jaH29uXOdyCm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805102247295Dc4ntP6vrhiAkfm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224729yXPt2DlU3eYqkzIT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224729U09Vw7XxYdnBHuC3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677262\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Commemorative Karl Marx Stamp by Thomas Mayfried</h3><p>为了纪念卡尔·马克思（Karl Marx）诞辰 200 周年，最近，德国邮政公司推出了由视觉艺术家 Thomas Mayfried 设计的纪念版主题邮票。为此德国联邦财政部还专门举办了一项邮票设计竞赛，Thomas Mayfried 正是获胜者。</p><p>邮票的设计使用了 1875 年英国摄影师 John Mayall 为其拍摄的标志性肖像照，这张照片也是马克思最为公众所熟悉的一张肖像照。Thomas Mayfried 用黑白线条的粗网格形式将马克思的形象作了艺术抽象化的处理。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224752baMR9rt5BjquFCPT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805102247529ZoKHNOlp17vUzsu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805102247525BwLzFuUIRhyWAQl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224752FECZtLOQHKzo2Ma5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224830ETKISRsnDGjtYLN2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.450667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/05/09/commemorative-karl-marx-stamp-thomas-mayfried-design-graphics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Frames Chair by Jaime Hayon for Expormim</h3><p>西班牙家具品牌 Expormim 为其藤制家具 Frames 系列再添新品，请来西班牙明星设计师 Jaime Hayon 设计了一组藤椅，全手工制作而成。每把椅子主体结构的座位和靠背部分，均由弯曲的去皮有色藤条制成，适用于那些精巧而个性十足的室内外空间。</p><p>所有的藤条都必须经过去皮、染料、涂底漆和表面涂层等几个步骤，一是为了美观，二则是保证椅子的抗晒性能。新品提供有扶手和无扶手两个版本，且有包括日本红、森林绿以及深蓝色等 11 种色彩选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224902whn7YHJmSgsDRaf3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224903zBT3bm2DKNWw9FgR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224903ArZXufsy2DwlWiGg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.155245\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224903uJWvNxr063eCO5HI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.109560\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224903MRg6xu7scSFptrkL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805102249036CFEoXgGYsUyeSzj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Portable Kitchen by Marc Sadler for Fabbrica Pelletterie Milano</h3><p>创办于 1946 年的意大利箱包品牌 Fabbrica Pelletterie Milano，多年来一直以创造具备高品质及设计感的商务休闲箱包著称。最近，奥地利设计师 Marc Sadler 为其 Bank 系列设计了新品，是一款便携式烹饪站，在米兰设计周第一次亮相。</p><p>如果仅从外表来看，它与一般的铝制外壳行李箱并无差些，但打开外壳的瞬间，就有一种“麻雀虽小五脏俱全”的感觉，内部配备了一个炉灶，一个迷你冰箱以及各种承担收纳存储功能的抽屉，意图为“现代游民”提供便携式的烹饪解决方案。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224931nXp0cgs3SoFeTdVK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644254\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224931AQIOgTvFDEJe8WGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805102249316Un9TrfN21ksXlxG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224931TOe37Xs9dftQzGRh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805102249325zCad4YrGkNFtKyE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.916064\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224932alAHe4zKuiMXDhkI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.826339\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510224932ieD1rBlp4yq7J2xc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.896996\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Trace Planter by Adam Goodrum for Tait </h3><p>悉尼设计师 Adam Goodrum 最近设计了一款名为 Trace 的种植器，是其为墨尔本家具设计品牌 Tait 的 Trace 户外休闲系列创造的新品。粉末涂层包裹的巨型铝制底盒，搭配向上延伸的网状结构，形成一个供不断向上生长的植物攀爬依附的结构，也更有助于帮助植物在生长过程中保持造型。</p><p>随着植物不断生长，Trace 就会变成一面小型绿植墙，还可以用作空间隔断。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225011cKb2AGHhX7lLI9zo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225011KyclJ9wD1TfzEYin.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225011fgJNeyPALd64GuVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225011DNqv05E8Cl6usPZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225011h62cuagjZCw8xLDT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225011YziE1F8Q7sfaqWkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/adam-goodrum-adds-the-trace-planter-to-outdoor-collection-for-tait/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Flutter by Paul Matter</h3><p>两年前，印度设计工作室 Paul Matter 推出了他们首个名为 TANGO的照明设备。最近他们又推出了一系列名为 Flutter 的摇臂灯，其实就是简化了的时钟样式，只剩下两条指针。</p><p>长长的旋转手臂连接在一个垂直的壁挂脊柱上，两支细长的手臂，可以创造出三种变体，用户可以根据实际需求将光源调整到合适的位置。它可以单独使用，也可以组合起来做成墙面装饰物，或是创造不同层次的光线需求。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805102250473xeHhUvPCBqQmy28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225047dIW1ZGKY6kwQb8DJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.154000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225047xP9UwiKvh1M0HmVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225048RqcUxnyjFuQDv2M7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225048kodzqHByibMLsxRT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225048b2NiZEUSBuGjmAeJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180510225048xm60lKsegopYnb2W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.568000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}